rnal-reference\" href=\"/topics/retinal-detachment/references/\">Sharma, 2015</a>], on loss of vision [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/retinal-detachment/references/\">Borooah, 2015</a>], and expert opinion in an ophthalmology textbook [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/retinal-detachment/references/\">Yanoff, 2013</a>].</p><!-- end field 13e9e4c4-8911-4320-a742-2d2260398424 --><!-- end item c177af57-dc6a-410f-b56c-065d15ff163a -->","subChapters":[]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}